{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"60bc7871dc2e4626e2aeb0","title":"2026-05-18 模式图标 BMP24→RGB565 压缩优化开发记录","desc":"","updated":1780371367059,"created":1780371330026,"custom":{},"fname":"开发记录.2026-05-18_模式图标BMP24转RGB565压缩优化开发记录","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"18385b7e03d4601254ca88d30cb94065","links":[],"anchors":{"2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录":{"type":"header","text":"2026-05-18 模式图标 BMP24→RGB565 压缩优化开发记录","value":"2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"需求背景":{"type":"header","text":"需求背景","value":"需求背景","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"优化目标":{"type":"header","text":"优化目标","value":"优化目标","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"涉及文件":{"type":"header","text":"涉及文件","value":"涉及文件","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"技术方案":{"type":"header","text":"技术方案","value":"技术方案","line":30,"column":0,"depth":2},"源格式bmp24":{"type":"header","text":"源格式（BMP24）","value":"源格式bmp24","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"目标格式rgb565":{"type":"header","text":"目标格式（RGB565）","value":"目标格式rgb565","line":41,"column":0,"depth":3},"转换算法":{"type":"header","text":"转换算法","value":"转换算法","line":50,"column":0,"depth":3},"lvgl-描述符变更":{"type":"header","text":"LVGL 描述符变更","value":"lvgl-描述符变更","line":65,"column":0,"depth":3},"压缩效果":{"type":"header","text":"压缩效果","value":"压缩效果","line":87,"column":0,"depth":2},"自动化工具":{"type":"header","text":"自动化工具","value":"自动化工具","line":101,"column":0,"depth":2},"注意事项":{"type":"header","text":"注意事项","value":"注意事项","line":118,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"jxzspjsfkjpyzxdrn5ntdy7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录\">2026-05-18 模式图标 BMP24→RGB565 压缩优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录-1\">2026-05-18 模式图标 BMP24→RGB565 压缩优化开发记录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2026-05-18-模式图标-bmp24rgb565-压缩优化开发记录-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"需求背景\">需求背景<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#需求背景\"></a></h2>\n<p>首页六模式图标（动漫、卡通、水墨画、线条画、简笔画、速写）原始采用 <strong>BMP24 格式嵌入 C 数组</strong>（<code>LV_IMG_CF_RAW</code>），每张 100×100 图片约 30 KB，六张合计约 <strong>180 KB 像素数据</strong>（C 源码文件约 1.1 MB）。在 BK7252N 这种资源受限的 MCU 上，Flash 和内存占用较大，需要进行压缩优化。</p>\n<h2 id=\"优化目标\">优化目标<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#优化目标\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>将六张模式图标的颜色格式从 <strong>BMP24（3 字节/像素）</strong> 转换为 <strong>RGB565（2 字节/像素）</strong></li>\n<li>去除 BMP 文件头（54 字节/张），输出为裸 RGB565 像素数组</li>\n<li>LVGL 颜色格式从 <code>LV_IMG_CF_RAW</code> 切换为 <code>LV_IMG_CF_TRUE_COLOR</code></li>\n<li>不影响显示效果（100×100 尺寸下 RGB565 视觉无差异）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"涉及文件\">涉及文件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#涉及文件\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>文件</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c</code></td><td><strong>优化后</strong>：RGB565 裸像素数组，约 724 KB</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.c.bak</code></td><td><strong>优化前备份</strong>：BMP24 完整格式，约 1.08 MB</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/mode_icons_bmp.h</code></td><td>头文件（无需修改，接口不变）</td></tr><tr><td><code>applications/images/convert_bmp_to_rgb565.py</code></td><td><strong>新增</strong>：一键转换脚本</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"技术方案\">技术方案<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#技术方案\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"源格式bmp24\">源格式（BMP24）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#源格式bmp24\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>BMP Header (54 bytes) + BGR888 pixels (bottom-up, row-padded to 4-byte)\n每像素 3 字节：B, G, R\n100×100 → 行字节 = ((100 * 3 + 3) / 4) * 4 = 304 bytes\n总数据 ≈ 54 + 304 * 100 = 30,454 bytes/张\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"目标格式rgb565\">目标格式（RGB565）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#目标格式rgb565\"></a></h3>\n<pre><code>裸像素数组 (top-down, no padding)\n每像素 2 字节：RGB565 (R5+G6+B5)\n100×100 → 100 * 100 * 2 = 20,000 bytes/张\n节省 ≈ 10,454 bytes/张 (34.3%)\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"转换算法\">转换算法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#转换算法\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">bgr888_to_rgb565</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> g<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token triple-quoted-string string\">\"\"\"BGR888 (BMP byte order) → RGB565\"\"\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>r <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">11</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>g <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>b <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>关键步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>解析 BMP 头，获取宽高、色深、像素偏移</li>\n<li>校验为 24-bit BMP</li>\n<li>从底行到顶行（BMP 存储顺序），逐像素做 BGR→RGB565 转换</li>\n<li>输出为 top-down 裸字节数组</li>\n<li>生成 LVGL 兼容的 C 数组代码，<code>header.cf = LV_IMG_CF_TRUE_COLOR</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"lvgl-描述符变更\">LVGL 描述符变更<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lvgl-描述符变更\"></a></h3>\n<pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 优化前</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> mode_icon_anime_bmp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> LV_IMG_CF_RAW<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// BMP24 原始格式</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>w <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>h <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">30054</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mode_icon_anime_bmp_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 优化后</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">lv_img_dsc_t</span> mode_icon_anime_bmp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> LV_IMG_CF_TRUE_COLOR<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// RGB565 标准格式</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>w <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>header<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>h <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">20000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> mode_icon_anime_bmp_map<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"压缩效果\">压缩效果<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#压缩效果\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>图片</th><th>原始 BMP24</th><th>RGB565</th><th>节省</th><th>压缩率</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>动漫 (anime)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td>卡通 (cartoon)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td>水墨画 (ink)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td>线条画 (line)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td>简笔画 (simple)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td>速写 (sketch)</td><td>30,054 B</td><td>20,000 B</td><td>10,054 B</td><td>33.5%</td></tr><tr><td><strong>合计</strong></td><td><strong>180,324 B</strong></td><td><strong>120,000 B</strong></td><td><strong>60,324 B</strong></td><td><strong>33.5%</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><strong>C 源文件级别</strong>：<code>mode_icons_bmp.c</code> 从 <strong>1,128,887 B → 742,146 B</strong>（含 C 语法开销），节省约 <strong>386 KB（34.3%）</strong>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"自动化工具\">自动化工具<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#自动化工具\"></a></h2>\n<p><code>convert_bmp_to_rgb565.py</code> 提供一键转换能力，后续新增或替换模式图标时可直接复用：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> applications/images\npython3 convert_bmp_to_rgb565.py\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 输入：mode_icons_bmp.c（BMP24 格式）</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 输出：mode_icons_bmp_opt.c（RGB565 格式）</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>脚本特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>自动解析 C 源码中的 BMP 数组和 LVGL 描述符</li>\n<li>校验 BMP 魔数、位深等合法性</li>\n<li>打印每张图片的转换详情和节省统计</li>\n<li>生成的 C 代码可直接替换原文件</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项\">注意事项<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#注意事项\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><code>LV_IMG_CF_TRUE_COLOR</code> vs <code>LV_IMG_CF_RAW</code></strong>：LVGL 对 <code>TRUE_COLOR</code> 格式有原生解码路径，显示性能与 <code>RAW</code> 一致，无额外开销</li>\n<li><strong>显示效果</strong>：100×100 尺寸下 RGB565 与 BMP24 肉眼无差异；若未来使用更大尺寸图片，需评估色阶损失</li>\n<li><strong>备份保留</strong>：原始 BMP24 文件已备份为 <code>mode_icons_bmp.c.bak</code>，如需回退可直接恢复</li>\n<li><strong>其他图片资源</strong>：<code>desktop_bmp.c</code>、<code>thermal_happy_lv.c</code> 等暂未转换，后续可参照此方案统一优化</li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI ��ӡ���̼��ĵ���","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"01a79b7e7f0264a5734e0abe50acd9de","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":96},"end":{"line":8,"column":28,"offset":121},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"������¼.��Ŀ������¼�ܸ�"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultN